components.name: Extract AirVisual Data
components.description: Calls the AirVisual API with latitude/longitude, checks PostgreSQL for existing records, and writes the JSON response atomically to a temporary file before renaming it.

components.name: Validate AirVisual JSON
components.description: Reads the JSON file produced by the extraction step, validates its structure and integrity, and logs confirmation before downstream processing.
outputs: Validated JSON data (in-memory)  passed to the loader

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful extraction of AirVisual data

components.name: Load AirVisual Data to PostgreSQL
components.description: Transforms the validated JSON into a dimensional model and inserts records into PostgreSQL dimension and fact tables, using ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING for idempotency.
inputs: Validated JSON data (in-memory) from validation step
outputs: Rows inserted into dimDateTimeTable, dimLocationTable, dimMainPollutionTable, factairvisualtable

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful validation of the JSON data
